node.text:
It’s been almost 2 WEEKS since
❤️‍🔥<lifE>❤️‍🔥dropped!! & I thought I’d do a little appreciation post for my seexxxyyy friends who spontaneously came to my studio session @electricladystudios and unleashed some riotgrrl realness on the mic (@xuulani) & the drums (@viobensmith) which ended up becoming the “F**K You” interlude on the album🤘🏾
These divine fairies aren’t musicians, they’re film makers but they sure as hell put that RAW EMOTION ON THE TRACK !! So much gratitude for these goddesses 🖤
